So yeah, here I sit. This would be what we call a short lived Saturday night seeing as Saturday night for me used to go on into the wee hours of the morning lol, like 5AM and shit. Don't miss the exhaustion, but goddamn, wouldn't it be better than sittin here?

As if you'd all care, lemme first say that I started the day at work! LOL Went okay, I'm finally hittin the sales floor! How nice is that? LOL I passed all my tests! Haha, my manager seems to be pretty impressed! CUZ I CHEATED! Haha, but hey, why not? It's all bullshit anyway!

Umm, I ran a couple miles today over in Cranford! What fun! My life is SOOO INTERESTING!!! I got nothin' else better to do anyway than run till I pass out and die! Maybe I'll get lucky one of these days? Let's cross our fingers shall we?

Beautiful surprise in Sewaren today! HA, how come when you want to escape certain things they come back and haunt you even months after you've left? Don't ask me, if I knew I wouldn't be askin the question! lol I'm so stupid and exhausted. HOWEVER I DID get to see my Boff tonight vistin from Monmouth University! I miss Boffmaster sooo fuckin much! I wish I was in college at the moment truthfully. But I guess it's all for the best after all.. got time to prepare before I hit up UCC in January lol. I can't wait! Ahaa!

So anyways, I dunno, life is bullshit at the moment. I'm borrred as usual.  I'm not a mental case LOL I swear, but I'm jus bummed out tonight. I have my days, unfortunately, tonight was one of them.

Figured out some shit tonight... but unfortunately a lot of shit that I could say is a little too personal for this PUBLIC journal. NOT THAT anyone would care ANYWAY!!!

Goddamn, I jus realized... I REALLY like the Trance Control songs. Ok but my mind is dead, this entry was supposed to be interesting, but guess what, as you've prolly noticed, IT'S NOT! BIG FUCKING SURPRISE!

LB3 isn't exactly an organization you want to tangle with... it could get you in big trouble... A little less from the austere side... I was thinking today about many things. Some days you wake up and wonder what the fuck is going on? I start questioning friends, life, people in general... it's all pretty stupid. I've recently discovered that I'm pretty fuckin jealous... I never realized that before... what is this sudden change in personality? In the past, I've always been the least jealous person I know... the most indifferent thinking of anybody. AND NOW... JEALOUSY. And it's a selfish jealousy too... in fact, it's straight up fuckin retarded! Maybe it's just me, but lately I feel like I got nobody... at least no one solid. And the one or two people that are solid, I fuckin blew off today and in the past... I dunno, we won't get into how long. Anyways, the one person I'm talking about, I usually talk to on a daily basis and have known all my life. SO I sense something... but it's hard to describe. I guess maybe it's too personal to write in this ONLINE journal where everyone can see... but sometimes I think it's all fake. Maybe I'm too posessive, maybe I'm just mental... but the fact is, any single person can do whatever the hell they want.. but when something comes up with this "person"... I take it personally and it drives me crazy. I hold higher standards in anything that's done... and when I feel like the person doesn't truly understand or isn't really there, I can't take the thoughts. So maybe it's time to take a step back for the sake of my dignity and detach myself emotionally from it all. BECAUSE, when it comes down to it, I realize there's people above me in their eyes and it only makes me feel stupid and inadequate. It's hard to put into words and I'm not about to go into detail so I'm trying to be general, but FUCK!! I'm pissed the fuck off... maybe I've been thinking too much... I think I'm falling into a hole of insanity with no way out or any means of escape. I guess I'll just let myself go until it's done and overwith... for now, I guess I have no choice but to keep on going. And now I look back on what I just wrote and it doesn't make sense, but that's ok, cuz it makes perfect sense to me! YOU JUST DON'T KNOW the in-between details. Haha, lately I wish I could live in the area of the sniper... someone shoot me... maybe I should resign my position within LB3.

Also I didn't appreciate my not feeling well being downplayed by an impressive performance of fucked-upness. I think the best medicine I could've had last night was to go hunting and shoot some birds... AND I AM NOT Talking about PHEASANT this time!
